    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "targets": "1 door, lock, or container",
    "text": "You make the target easier to open. *Knock* grants a +4 status bonus to any creature that tries to open the target door, lock, or container with an Athletics or a Thievery check. You can attempt a Thievery check to open the target as part of casting *knock*, and you add your level even if you're untrained.  \n  \n *Knock* counteracts *lock*.",
